description: Frontend React testing conventions
globs: frontend/**/*.{ts,tsx}
alwaysApply: false
---

# Frontend testing

- Use Vitest and Testing Library; avoid testing implementation details.
- Mock `fetch` or the `api` client at module boundaries.
- Use helpers from `frontend/src/test/test-utils.tsx` when components need providers.
- Prefer testing extracted pure functions (for example `src/lib/proxyPayload.ts`) for form mapping logic.
